Class GraphNodeNeighborsCache<N extends GraphNode<N,​E>,​E extends GraphEdge<N,​E>>

    public class GraphNodeNeighborsCache<N extends GraphNode<N,​E>,​E extends GraphEdge<N,​E>>
extends Object
    This class represents a cache used in the Graph class for A* to improve runtime. It maps Nodes to a list of their neighbors.
